dct_title_s: Map of a portion of the Upper Scioto River Basin  showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Scioto River Basin (Part upper portion)
dct_description_sm: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks of the upper Scioto River Basin and quality of underground water.
Scale bar lower right corner of map.
